  "texts": [
    "This bias is present in the model as well.",
    "Figure 4 illustrates this problem.",
    "The values in the \"ART:Hypothesis\" column are generally low and often even zero.",
    "Thus, this class is rarely predicted.",
    "The row for that class shows that even sentences with that ground truth label are often predicted as other, more common ART classes such as \"ART:Conclusion\" or \"ART:Result\".The classes for the generic dataset described in Sect. 5.5 are based on the general rhetorical structure of research papers and are derived from ontologies such as [19,35,82]."
  ],
